<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
  <div class="hero relative" style="min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);">
    <%= image_tag "sova_recon_bolt.png", class: "absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" %>

    <div class="hero-overlay bg-black bg-opacity-20 relative z-10"></div>

    <div class="hero-content text-neutral-content text-center relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <h1 class="mb-5 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white">V-TACTICS</h1>
        <p class="mb-14 text-white">
          VALORANTプレイヤーにとって、<br>
          初心者にはわかりづらく、慣れたプレイヤーでも決まった行動をしがちな<br>
          「定点」をすぐに引き出せるサービス。
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <%= link_to "まずは、色んな「定点」を見てみる！", techniques_path, class: "btn bg-valorant-color text-white border-valorant-color" %>
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <%= link_to "お気に入り登録した「定点」を見る（マイページへ）", favorites_technique_path(current_user.id), class: "btn btn-info" %>
          <% else %>
            <%= link_to "新規登録して「定点」を追加する", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-info" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll_down" id="type07">
    <a href="#">
      <div class="arrow"></div>
      <div class="arrow"></div>
      <div class="arrow"></div>
      <span class="text">Scroll</span>
    </a>
  </div>
  <p class="text-gray-500 animate-bounce"><i class="fa-solid fa-angles-down"></i></p>
</div>

